Class NamedQuery

java.lang.Object
  org.objectstyle.cayenne.query.IndirectQuery
      org.objectstyle.cayenne.query.NamedQuery
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable, Query
public class NamedQuery
extends IndirectQuery

A query that is a reference to a named parameterized query stored in the mapping. The actual query is resolved during execution.

Since:
1.2
Author:
Andrus Adamchik
